title: 5: BLACKING OUT @ FSU, Getting the FRAT FLU, and the Worst of it all Eating Disorders
description: Sadie has taken a week off, not because it was planned, she came down with the “Frat Flu.” Sadie found herself on her deathbed with the flu a few days after visiting her brother in college and she’s hear now to tell you all about it. She discuses how her weekend played out while visiting her brother and dives into another big topic that plays a role inter life, eating disorders. Listen in to hear all about it.
